{"tid":1586857,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[包容體諒] 「小心分化割席」戒備信號現正生效","createTime":"2019-09-22T07:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T07:25:11.000Z","uid":2634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"179302de007a4323c074474d69a923b1ec833534","tid":1586857,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"場運動可以行到今日喺因為各路手足<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不分化、絕不割席、絕不篤灰</strong></span></span></div><br />\n請大家繼續堅守，唔好俾三毛同有心人分化到<br />\n<br />\n致勇武手足：請體諒和理非手足思想未能跟上前線，話曬喺第一次突破咗心理關口，和理非喺會慢慢學習同改進。<br />\n致和理非手足：請相信前線手足嘅決定，唔好因為自己一貫底線立場而否定前線手足嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋學識互相包容同體諒，我哋就會越團結，場運動就越強大。相反，如果我哋手足之間互相猜忌，行返2014條舊路，對家就可以將我哋<strong>逐一擊破</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「一枝竹仔會易折彎，幾枝竹一扎段折難。」</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化、不割席、不篤灰</div></span></span></strong><br />\n請幫推 多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ed96b66bb417a187ec8f478fddb0d021d9734c","tid":1586857,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1a4bcb486c6a1d6cdc3ab5d73d9445f753adac8","tid":1586857,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"867bf43f937cc2c8352b32eadcfc64957921696c","tid":1586857,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:12:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a7d95383009c05f1b995011accea4ad0991a2cd","tid":1586857,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b157940fb02cc088456bf97f305bd6abd578e3c","tid":1586857,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc